{"tid":1014413,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"係得茶餐廳做侍應智力一般低過正常人","createTime":"2019-02-09T07:28:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-09T08:40:05.000Z","uid":171594,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a7625aecbbcbf1c2027425c5ec635f598f21ac1e","tid":1014413,"uid":171594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T07:28:26.000Z","msg":"做侍應都算係正當職業<br />\n但係茶餐廳做個班真係普遍蠢啲 反應遲鈍啲<br />\n食茶餐廳已經唔會期望有咩服務態度<br />\n但求正正常常食餐飯就算<br />\n做呢啲工已經唔使做啲咩複雜野<br />\n但都可以錯漏百出<br />\n成間野得個幾檯客<br />\n人手已經有幾個<br />\n就算炒場都唔會忙得去邊<br />\n但都成日落錯單 出錯餐<br />\nTake張普通order都要個客重複講幾次<br />\n做清潔又求撚其<br />\n我知你份人工唔方會好高<br />\n但都起碼做返本份 做足啲基本野啦<br />\n唔想做就轉工啦"},{"pid":"16c51316352ed55da61c6991d164827c591d29f6","tid":1014413,"uid":192491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T07:35:06.000Z","msg":"禾做侍應關你撚事呀？"},{"pid":"23473f6141a7a911d1eb1a362d833a109070889d","tid":1014413,"uid":58307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T07:47:48.000Z","msg":"高過你"},{"pid":"fb437395d5b755a3382b54dc9047ac332e257a84","tid":1014413,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T07:48:56.000Z","msg":"再嘈就加你料！🖕"},{"pid":"f798d125c7632302afba394c82dc6512bda5b7eb","tid":1014413,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T07:49:39.000Z","msg":"話我？<br />\n加你料呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4365da56d718223e050caffb8c07203d981216c8","tid":1014413,"uid":14350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T08:40:05.000Z","msg":"正常人轉晒工"}]}